    <!-- Chosen Palette: Warm Neutral Harmony -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A non-linear, interactive portfolio design. The structure prioritizes immediate impact by leading with a KPI dashboard of key achievements. This is followed by an interactive vertical timeline for professional experience, a visual radar chart for skills with filtering capabilities, and a clean section for education. A sticky navigation bar enables easy movement between these thematic sections. This dashboard-and-drill-down approach was chosen to make the CV scannable for high-level impact (for busy recruiters) while allowing for deep dives into specific areas of interest, making the experience more engaging and user-directed than a static document. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Key Achievements -> Goal: Impress & Inform -> Viz: Interactive KPI cards -> Interaction: Hover to show details. Justification: Highlights quantifiable impact immediately. Method: HTML/CSS/JS.
        - Professional Experience -> Goal: Show Chronology & Detail -> Viz: Interactive Vertical Timeline -> Interaction: Click to expand/collapse job details. Justification: Organizes dense information cleanly, preventing cognitive overload and encouraging exploration. Method: HTML/CSS/JS.
        - Skills -> Goal: Compare & Organize -> Viz: Radar Chart & Filterable Lists -> Interaction: Chart for visual summary, buttons to filter and display detailed skill lists. Justification: Provides a quick visual gauge of competencies and allows users to pull only the specific information they need. Library: Chart.js.
        - Education & Certs -> Goal: Inform -> Viz: Clean Card Layout. -> Interaction: None. Justification: Clear, static presentation for foundational information. Method: HTML/CSS.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
